ionMeasureCalculations.java** - Internal class containing the core measure calculation logic, uses both BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer and VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer\n3. **FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java** - Public API for FX vanilla option trade calculations with DEFAULT instances using both Black and Vanna-Volga pricers\n\n## CSV Plugin Loader (modules/loader/)\n\nFound 1 loader plugin under modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/:\n- **FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java** - Implements TradeCsvParserPlugin and TradeCsvWriterPlugin<FxVanillaOptionTrade>, handles CSV format parsing and writing for FX vanilla option trades\n\n## Barrier Option Embedding FxVanillaOption (modules/product/)\n\nFound FxSingleBarrierOption class under modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/:\n- **FxSingleBarrierOption.java** - Barrier option product that embeds FxVanillaOption as a dependency field (@PropertyDefinition field `underlyingOption` of type FxVanillaOption). This class is also annotated with @BeanDefinition and implements FxOptionProduct and Resolvable<ResolvedFxSingleBarrierOption>.\n\nThe FxVanillaOption type family forms the foundation for both direct vanilla option pricing and as a component of barrier option products in Strata's FX options module."
